    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <title>[Lumeos] Password Reset </title>
</head>
<body style="margin:0; background-color: #f8fbfd; height: 100%; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">
    <div>
        <p>Your username is:</p>
        <%= username %>
        <p>Please note: The link below only work from your mobile phone. If you are on your laptop or desktop please go to your mobile phone to view this email and then click the link below from your mobile phone.</p>
        <p>Visit this <a href="<%= HOST + link %>">link</a> to restore your password:</p>
        <p>Please do not reply to this email as this address is not monitored.</p>
        <p>If you are having a problem with your account, please email team@lumeos.io</p>
        <p>Thank you for using our app!</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
